# FleetPulse Dashboard Rules

## Data Binding (CRITICAL - NEVER FORGET)

- ALWAYS use `@Input()` with explicit types: `@Input() data!: DataType`
- ALWAYS provide defaults: `@Input() title: string = ''`
- NEVER use `any` - always type inputs properly
- Import `Input` from `@angular/core`

## FleetPulse Theme

- Colors: Primary #5ad85a, Accent #6ee755, Dark bg #050505/#0a0c0a
- Status: Optimal #6ee755, Warning #eab308, Critical #ef4444
- Support dark/light theme toggle

## Component Pattern

- Standalone components: `standalone: true`
- Fleet metrics: vehicles, routes, maintenance, costs
- Green gradient charts, fleet-specific data visualizations
- Transform generic dashboard to fleet management context

## Files Context

- Dashboard: `Spruha/src/app/components/dashboard/dashboard/`
- Colors: `Spruha/public/assets/scss/_variables.scss`
- Charts: `Spruha/src/app/shared/data/dashboard.ts`
